🚨 Winner Alert 🚨 
Congratulations @ollierodgers1 🍾 Thanks to your Remix Fix, Malto can once again listen to the music 🎶 Ollie wins a Girl Films™ prize pack, and will have his edit uploaded to CrailTube with the rest of the original video as Doll V2. Thank you to all who entered. It was not easy to choose. 
#MaltoDollRemixFix
#DOLLtheGirlVideo
